Замена: \(2^x=t,t>0\)
$$\frac{t+8}{t-8}+\frac{t-8}{t+8}-\frac{16\cdot t+96}{t^2-64}\geq 0\\ \frac{t+8}{t-8}+\frac{t-8}{t+8}-\frac{16t+96}{(t-8)(t+8)}\geq 0\\ \frac{((t+8)^2+(t-8)^2-16t-96)}{(t-8)(t+8)}\geq 0\\ \frac{t^2+16t+64+t^2-16t+64-16t-96}{(t-8)(t+8)}\geq 0\\ \frac{2t^2-16t+32}{(t-8)(t+8)}\geq 0\\ \frac{t^2-8t+16}{(t-8)(t+8)}\geq 0\\ \frac{(t-4)^2}{(t-8)(t+8)}\geq 0$$
$$\displaystyle \left[ \begin{array}{l l}
t=4\\
t >8
\end{array} \right.$$
Обратная замена:
$$\displaystyle \begin{array}{{>{\displaystyle}l}}
\left[ \begin{array}{l l}
2^{x} =4\\
2^{x} >8
\end{array} \right.\\
\left[ \begin{array}{l l}
2^{x} =2^{2}\\
2^{x} >2^{3}
\end{array} \right.\\
\left[ \begin{array}{l l}
x=2\\
x >3
\end{array} \right.\\
\end{array}$$
Ответ: \(x\in (3;+\infty)~\cup\) {\(2\)}
